snippet.title: Azure Striker GUNVOLT 2 - The 2nd Trailer
snippet.description:
Azure Striker Gunvolt 2 hits the Nintendo 3DS eShop on September 30, 2016! 

In this second trailer, we introduce the entire cast of the game, including the 7 boss characters of the nefarious The Seven. You can also meet the members of Gunvolt and Copen's teams, and get a taste of everyone's abilities!

A formidable new enemy awaits. Are you up for the challenge?
